description: Applies a security group to the association between the target network and the Client VPN endpoint. This action replaces the existing security groups with the specified security groups.

parameters.name: ClientVpnEndpointId
parameters.description: The ID of the Client VPN endpoint.

parameters.name: VpcId
parameters.description: The ID of the VPC in which the associated target network is located.

parameters.name: SecurityGroupIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the security groups to apply to the associated target network. Up to 5 security groups can be applied to an associated target network. (string) ---

nested_items.name: SecurityGroupIds
nested_items.description: The IDs of the applied security groups.
